      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">TOP-TIPS</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true">This topic includes all of the best </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Top-Tips</text><text styleclass="Normal" translate="true"> to be published when it has more than five. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Top-Tip 1</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Save you model</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">...</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">A: Save new model immediately</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">: then Auto-Save will also start immediately.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">B: CTRL+S</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> to save the latest major change.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">C: Save as ...</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> NEW model-name if you open a model you do not want to change. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:2px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Top-Tip 2</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> : When to set </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">CYCLES / Min = 0</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> :</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">&#32;</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">CYCLES / MIN = 0.0001</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> to design </text><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">stationary</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> mechanisms.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">To eliminate forces that result from a mechanisms motion, set the Cycling Speed to ~0. &#160;Then, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Inertia</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Centrifugal</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">, and </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Coriolis</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> forces are ~0.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">For example: Scissor Lift, Guard Balancing, Counter-weight Balancing.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:2px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Top-Tip 3</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true"> : </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">RIGHT-CLICK to SELECT and &apos;OK&apos; a command</text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="VariableName-indent"><text styleclass="VariableName-indent" translate="true">Right-click the LAST Command-Manager element and also do a command.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">For example: </text><text styleclass="T_Menu" translate="true">Click ADD Trace-Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">, </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Right-Click a Point</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> - and there it is!</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
